{"tid":2424864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重返亞洲】新英日同盟，英國航母伊莉莎白女王號進駐南海","createTime":"2021-02-27T03:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T21:56:15.000Z","uid":229777,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c514398fdd7a08a2a7faa0825ceeb8e31dc6543d","tid":2424864,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"英國航母伊莉莎白女王號進入南海，準備同日本軍演，預備建立更深入盟友關係以應對中國及北韓威脅，預料此舉會刺激與英國正因香港問題交惡嘅中國<br />\n<br />\n同時英國有打算加入日澳美印嘅四方安全對話QUAD，圍堵中國<br />\n<br />\n英國派航母嚟南海，預計目的為控制中國對區域安全所造成嘅威脅，同時亦係對中國無視中英聯合聲明，損害香港獨特性嘅回應<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thehill.com/opinion/national-security/540483-britain-is-back-in-asia-sending-a-message-to-beijing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fopinion%2Fnational-security%2F540483-britain-is-back-in-asia-sending-a-message-to-beijing&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=7b44154a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thehill.com/opinion/national-security/540483-britain-is-back-in-asia-sending-a-message-to-beijing</a>"},{"pid":"d2bbc622121beaa4f395d9ae82d252d3ee252bf8","tid":2424864,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06bcd32ac8576be776ff7725092f64abdccd67a2","tid":2424864,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b728fce44ce5d022ba4a96f51ba671865c7ba0c3","tid":2424864,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"408672019408a14ddb75e2069e96e85a4cdbdca0","tid":2424864,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T21:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s